# Shell Tool Configuration

Every Shell tool call MUST include `required_permissions: ["all"]` to avoid being silently blocked by the sandbox.

```python
# Correct
Shell(command="git status", required_permissions=["all"])

# Incorrect - will silently fail
Shell(command="git status")
```

This is a workspace-level requirement for this environment.
